      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 260,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# UI / Interaction Library\n\nThis package captures authored UI structure and interaction semantics without collapsing into a generic builder.\n\nV1 classes:\n- `ui-view` (generic substrate)\n- `port-view`\n- `icon-view`\n- `document-view`\n- `summary-view` (legacy compatibility)\n- `editor-view`\n- `panel`\n- `control`\n- `ui-state` (labelled `State`)\n- `binding`\n- `route`\n\nDeferred:\n- `browser-view`\n- `modal`\n- `layout-region`\n- `feedback`\n- `theme-token`",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
