    {
      "id": "ui-interaction-root-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Runtime Pressure",
      "position": {
        "x": 1040,
        "y": 220
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 240,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Runtime Pressure\n\nLikely typed relationships:\n- `Port View` is consumed by host ports\n- `Icon View` carries semantic zoom identity\n- `Document View` carries readable artifact meaning\n- `Summary View` remains migration compatibility for older readable surfaces\n- `Panel` contains `Control`\n- `Binding` binds `Control` to `State`\n- `Route` navigates to a view surface\n\nKeep the nodeset focused on semantics, not styling or builder chrome.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
